{"doc":{"isMarkdown":true,"isTranslated":true,"isActive":true,"flaws":{},"title":"<mrow>","mdn_url":"/zh-CN/docs/Web/MathML/Element/mrow","locale":"zh-CN","native":"中文 (简体)","sidebarHTML":"\n    <ol>\n        <li><strong><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/MathML/Element\">MathML Reference</a></strong>\n\n        \n            </li><li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/MathML/Element/maction\">&lt;maction&gt;</a></li>\n        \n            <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/MathML/Element/math\">&lt;math&gt;</a></li>\n        \n            <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/MathML/Element/menclose\">&lt;menclose&gt;</a></li>\n        \n            <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/MathML/Element/merror\">&lt;merror&gt;</a></li>\n        \n            <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/MathML/Element/mfenced\">&lt;mfenced&gt;</a></li>\n        \n            <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/MathML/Element/mfrac\">&lt;mfrac&gt;</a></li>\n        \n            <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/MathML/Element/mi\">&lt;mi&gt;</a></li>\n        \n            <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/MathML/Element/mmultiscripts\">&lt;mmultiscripts&gt;</a></li>\n        \n            <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/MathML/Element/mn\">&lt;mn&gt;</a></li>\n        \n            <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/MathML/Element/mo\">&lt;mo&gt;</a></li>\n        \n            <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/MathML/Element/mover\">&lt;mover&gt;</a></li>\n        \n            <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/MathML/Element/mpadded\">&lt;mpadded&gt;</a></li>\n        \n            <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/MathML/Element/mphantom\">&lt;mphantom&gt;</a></li>\n        \n            <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/MathML/Element/mroot\">&lt;mroot&gt;</a></li>\n        \n            <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/MathML/Element/mrow\">&lt;mrow&gt;</a></li>\n        \n            <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/MathML/Element/ms\">&lt;ms&gt;</a></li>\n        \n            <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/MathML/Element/mspace\">&lt;mspace&gt;</a></li>\n        \n            <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/MathML/Element/msqrt\">&lt;msqrt&gt;</a></li>\n        \n            <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/MathML/Element/mstyle\">&lt;mstyle&gt;</a></li>\n        \n            <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/MathML/Element/msub\">&lt;msub&gt;</a></li>\n        \n            <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/MathML/Element/msubsup\">&lt;msubsup&gt;</a></li>\n        \n            <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/MathML/Element/msup\">&lt;msup&gt;</a></li>\n        \n            <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/MathML/Element/mtable\">&lt;mtable&gt;</a></li>\n        \n            <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/MathML/Element/mtd\">&lt;mtd&gt;</a></li>\n        \n            <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/MathML/Element/mtext\">&lt;mtext&gt;</a></li>\n        \n            <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/MathML/Element/mtr\">&lt;mtr&gt;</a></li>\n        \n            <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/MathML/Element/munder\">&lt;munder&gt;</a></li>\n        \n            <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/MathML/Element/munderover\">&lt;munderover&gt;</a></li>\n        \n            <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/MathML/Element/semantics\">&lt;semantics&gt;</a></li>\n        \n\n        \n    </ol>\n","body":[{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<p>MathML <code>&lt;mrow&gt;</code> 元素用于对连续多行表达式的不同子表达式进行分组，一条子表达式通常算作一行，至少包含一或多个<a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/MathML/Element/mo\" class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\">操作符 (en-US)</a>与其运算对象（比如 <code><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/MathML/Element/mi\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" class=\"only-in-en-us\">&lt;mi&gt; (en-US)</a></code> 和 <code><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/MathML/Element/mn\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" class=\"only-in-en-us\">&lt;mn&gt; (en-US)</a></code>）。此元素呈现为包含其内容的水平行。</p>\n<p>在编写 MathML 表达式时，您应该使用 <code>&lt;mrow&gt;</code> 将表达式中的元素分组，就像它们在数学解释时的分成一行行一样。正确的分组有助于表达式的呈现，具体体现在以下几个方面：</p>\n<ul>\n  <li>如果有需要，它会改变间距来改善显示效果。</li>\n  <li>它允许采用更明智的断行和缩进算法。</li>\n  <li>通过自动化系统，如计算机代数系统和音频渲染器（automated systems such as computer algebra systems and audio renderers），它能简化表达式的解释（interpretation）过程。</li>\n</ul>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"属性","title":"属性","isH3":false,"content":"<dl>\n  <dt id=\"class_id_style\">class, id, style</dt>\n  <dd>\n    <p>用来供<a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/CSS\">样式表</a>使用。</p>\n  </dd>\n  <dt id=\"dir\">dir</dt>\n  <dd>\n    <p>行内公式的书写方向。可能的值为 <code>ltr</code>（自左向右）或 <code>rtl</code>（自右向左）。</p>\n  </dd>\n  <dt id=\"href\">href</dt>\n  <dd>\n    <p>用于设置一个指向指定的 URI 的超链接。</p>\n  </dd>\n  <dt id=\"mathbackground\">mathbackground</dt>\n  <dd>\n    <p>背景色。支持 <code>#rgb</code>、<code>#rrggbb</code> 和 <a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/CSS/color_value#color_keywords\" class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\">HTML 颜色 (en-US)</a>。</p>\n  </dd>\n  <dt id=\"mathcolor\">mathcolor</dt>\n  <dd>\n    <p>文本颜色。支持 <code>#rgb</code>、<code>#rrggbb</code> 和 <a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/CSS/color_value#color_keywords\" class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\">HTML 颜色 (en-US)</a>。</p>\n  </dd>\n</dl>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"示例","title":"示例","isH3":false,"content":"<div class=\"code-example\"><pre class=\"brush: html notranslate\"><code><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>math</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n\n  <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>mrow</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n    <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>mn</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span> 1 <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>mn</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n    <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>mo</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span> + <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>mo</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n    <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>mn</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span> 1 <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>mn</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n  <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>mrow</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n\n  <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>mrow</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n    <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>mo</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span> ( <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>mo</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n    <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>mrow</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n      <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>mi</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span> x <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>mi</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n      <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>mo</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span> , <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>mo</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n      <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>mi</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span> y <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>mi</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n    <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>mrow</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n    <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>mo</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span> ) <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>mo</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n  <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>mrow</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n\n<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>math</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n</code></pre></div>"}},{"type":"specifications","value":{"title":"规范","id":"规范","isH3":false,"specifications":[{"bcdSpecificationURL":"https://w3c.github.io/mathml-core/#horizontally-group-sub-expressions-mrow","title":"MathML Core"}],"query":"mathml.elements.mrow"}},{"type":"browser_compatibility","value":{"title":"浏览器兼容性","id":"浏览器兼容性","isH3":false,"query":"mathml.elements.mrow","dataURL":"/zh-CN/docs/Web/MathML/Element/mrow/bcd.json"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"参见","title":"参见","isH3":false,"content":"<ul>\n  <li>HTML 分组元素：<a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/HTML/Element/div\"><code>&lt;div&gt;</code></a></li>\n</ul>"}}],"toc":[{"text":"属性","id":"属性"},{"text":"示例","id":"示例"},{"text":"规范","id":"规范"},{"text":"浏览器兼容性","id":"浏览器兼容性"},